New York State 1892 Census returns for Brooklyn's 15th election district

This collection consists of two volumes containing 1892 New York State Census returns from Brooklyn's 15th election district. For each name, the returns record various demographic data, including sex, age, color, country of birth, citizenship status, and occupation.
